this_title: UFOs at the Zoo: The Flaming Lips Live in Oklahoma City
introduction: Recorded live in Oklahoma City September 15, 2006.This disc is a "Music Video Interactive" which contains DVD video of the entire concert, 256kbps MP3s of the show, as well as hyper links to downloadable content such as ringtones, wallpapers, IM icons, and bonus video clips as they become available.
